{"tid":995411,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解佢地去親邊到邊到都會撞到鬼","createTime":"2019-01-25T11:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T12:35:49.000Z","uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d07e9293c6d9838b5cbbdfe117a235871ac9628","tid":995411,"uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hzL_O6gVqDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhzL_O6gVqDw&d=2zg5K6sz%2BK3wx%2BOtRjj9UMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=50240272\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hzL_O6gVqDw</a><br />\n戴耳機開大聲啲睇<br />\n3:38-5:27隻鬼係衣櫃到 係咁抓個衣櫃 又搖啲衣架 仲要唔避人<br />\n9:22-9:40佢地個聽到上面嗰層有啲dum dum聲 突然係上層揼咗個波落嚟 條友即刻衝上去<br />\n11:14-11:35 左面窗口左下角有個白影 突然屈身?向下走咗 因為嗰到行一步都會有好大回音 但係就係點聽極都冇第三個人嘅腳步聲<br />\n18:45-19:42 個人同隻鬼對話緊 問佢係點死 隻鬼閂門拒絕 慢慢拉低掛咗係門口條褲 個人第一時間踢門衝入去 但係人影鬼影冇隻"},{"pid":"4071b9bacbce7efdf718fa94151b40d63fef01a0","tid":995411,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"造假咪得"},{"pid":"7b21550b906490702ad60ac4c0b3b5b0632890e0","tid":995411,"uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4071b9bacbce7efdf718fa94151b40d63fef01a0","tid":995411,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"造假咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"一開頭個個都係咁諗掛啦<br />\n但係造假都要有第三個人在場先造到㗎<br />\n有冇啲實證 或者假設<br />\n我好似中撚咗毒咁 依加日日睇 快啲救我出嚟<br />\n畀啲理由我"},{"pid":"73e3fe1dba21e47331f9e0828efd3b67ad13ed69","tid":995411,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"造假"},{"pid":"c15949f825926b8ec093c8eb03cede6ba5f9a39d","tid":995411,"uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73e3fe1dba21e47331f9e0828efd3b67ad13ed69","tid":995411,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"造假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"